name: The Year of the TIGER
description:
A lot of hopes are being lifted in this year, after these past 2 years we got dumped because of the pandemic.
Our Tiger soul are rising in this year!
We have to conquer the Tiger and become one!
The pure soul starts to lift the conciousness.

"Mang" "Ang" "Ung" are the Triaksara from the balinesse sacred scriptures that splitted from the main aksara "Ong" the "nothingness"

Mang Ang Ung become one turns to "MAUNG" / "MONG" (MONK) or so called the TIGER,

Let's put the hope within the TIGER in our soul to get better in this year!
